quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  36,60,Angizange yini nginiphoqe Oh bantwana ba-Adam! Ukuthi ningamkhonzi usathane? Ngempela yena uyisitha senu esigqamile
  36,61,Nokuthi nikhonze mina? Lena yindlela elungile
  36,62,Futhi ngempela wadukisa iqembu elikhulu phakathi kwenu ngakube naningenawo yini umqondo
  36,63,Lesi yisihogo enanethenjiswe sona
  36,64,Ngenani kusona namhlanje ngenxa yokuthi naningakholwa
  36,65,Kulolusuku siyayisicilela imilomo yabo futhi izandla zabo zizokhuluma nezinyawo zabo zizofakaza mayelana naloko ababekusebenzela
  36,66,Futhi ukube besithanda besizosusa amehlo abo bese beyaphuphutheka endleleni bese bebona kanjani
  36,67,Futhi ukube besithanda besizobaguqula ezindaweni zabo bebengeke besakwazi ukuya phambili nokuphindela emumva
  36,68,"Futhi noma ngabe ngubani esimnika impilo ende simhlehlisela emumva endalweni, ngakube abanawo yini umqondo na"
  36,69,"Futhi asimfundisanga ubumbongi futhi akumfanele, yona ayiyilutho ngaphandle kwesikhumbuzo neQur’an ecacile"
  36,70,Ukuze ixwayise noma ngabe ngubani ophilayo futhi kuqiniseke izwi ukubhekana nabangakholwa
  36,71,Ababoni yini ukuthi sabadalela kuloko okwenziwe yizandla zethu izinkomo abangabanini bazo na
  36,72,Futhi sabathobisela zona ngakho-ke ezinye phakathi kwazo bayazigibela futhi ezinye phakathi kwazo bayazidla
  36,73,"Futhi banenzuzo kuzona kanye neziphuzo, ngakube ababongi yini na"
  36,74,Futhi esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi bazithathela izithixo ukuze mhlawumbe bathole usizo
  36,75,Azikwazi ukubasiza futhi bona kuzona bayibutho elilethwe ngaphambili
  36,76,Ngakho-ke ayingakuphathi kabi inkulumo yabo ngempela thina siyakwazi lokho abakufihlayo kanye nalokho abakuveza obala
  36,77,Ngakube umuntu akaboni yini ukuthi samdala ngeconsi lesidoda kulapho yena eyisitha esigqamile
  36,78,"Futhi wasenzela isibonelo wakhohlwa yindalo yakhe wathi, “ngubani onika amathambo impilo uma esewuthuli na?”"
  36,79,"Ithi, “uwanika impilo lowo owadalayo ngesikhathi sokuqala futhi yena uyisazi sazona zonke izidalwa”"
  36,80,Lowo owanibekela umlilo esihlahleni esiluhlaza kulapho nina nokhela kuwona
  36,81,Angeke yini lowo owadala amazulu nomhlaba akwazi ukudala okufana nabo na? Yebo! Yena ungumdali owaziyo
  36,82,"Kuphela, impoqo yakhe, uma ehlose into ethize uthi kuyona “yenzeka” bese iyenzeka"
  36,83,Ngakho-ke udumo malube kulowo esandleni sakhe ekunombuso wezinto zonke futhi niyophindiselwa kuyena
  37,1,Ngalabo abahlelwe ngezigaba
  37,2,Ngalabo abahambisa amafu ngendlela enhle
  37,3,Ngalabo abafunda isikhumbuzo
  37,4,Ngempela uMvelinqangi wenu munye
  37,5,INkosi yamazulu nomhlaba kanye nako konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili neNkosi yempumalanga
  37,6,Ngempela thina salihlobisa izulu eliseduzane ngomhlobiso wezinkanyezi
  37,7,"Nokulondolozwa\tkwalo\tmayelana\tnabobonke\tosathane abahlubukayo"
  37,8,Abakwazi ukulalela inhlangano ephakeme kakhulu futhi bajikijelwa kuwona wonke amacala
  37,9,Bayaxoshwa futhi okwabo yisijeziso sangunaphakade
  37,10,Ngaphandle kwalowo ohlwitha okuthize ngokuntshontsha bese elandelwa yilangabi lomlilo elihlabayo
  37,11,Ngakho-ke babuze ukuthi ngakube yibona yini abanzima ekudaleni noma yilabo esabadalayo na? Ngempela thina sabadala ngobumba olunamathelayo
  37,12,Kepha uyamangala kulapho benza inhlekisa
  37,13,Futhi uma bekhunjuziswa abakhumbuli
  37,14,Futhi uma bebona uphawu benza inhlekisa
  37,15,"Futhi\tbathi,\t“lokhu\takuyilutho\tngaphandle\tkomlingo ogqamile”"
  37,16,Ngakube uma sesifile saphenduka uthuli namathambo ngempela siyovuswa yini na
  37,17,Kanye nobaba bethu basendulo na
  37,18,"Ithi, “yebo futhi nina niyothotshiswa"
  37,19,Kuyoba ukukhala okukodwa kuphela kulapho bona bebhekile
  37,20,"Futhi bayothi, “Oh usizi kuthina! lolu wusuku lwenhlawulo”"
  37,21,Lolu wusuku lokugcina enaniluphika